*   **Mindfulness/Meditation (5-15 minutes):**  Even a short period of meditation or deep breathing can make a huge difference.
    *   **Why it works:** Reduces stress, improves focus, promotes mental clarity, and cultivates a more positive mindset.
    *   **Tip:**  Use a guided meditation app (Headspace, Calm, Insight Timer) if you're a beginner.
